-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

The optical directory of RIPL-3 contains the files required for preparing
inputs for optical model calculations and, in addition, one microscopic
optical model code. The optical/ directory contains the phenomenological 
OMP library and a library of deformation parameters useful for, e.g., DWBA
calculations. It also contains a code for obtaining alpha-particle potentials
in standard format, using a built-in model and volume integrals. 

The directory is divided into four sub-directories, as follows:
 
